    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Organisms that live in or on another, from which they obtain nutrients and, frequently, shelter at the expense of the host organism, which it may directly or indirectly harm.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
